nl.tue.geometrycore.datastructures.doublylinkedlist

Class DoublyLinkedListItem<TItem extends DoublyLinkedListItem>

  • java.lang.Object
    • nl.tue.geometrycore.datastructures.doublylinkedlist.DoublyLinkedListItem<TItem>
  • Type Parameters:
    TItem - class of items for the list, typically, the inheriting class
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    ReferencedDLLItem

    public class DoublyLinkedListItem<TItem extends DoublyLinkedListItem>
extends java.lang.Object
    Base class for storing objects in a DoublyLinkedList. Note that every object can be stored in at most one list. We do not keep track of which list an object is stored in, for sake of efficiency.
